                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17290827-32-defend156 t17290827-32-defloc145"></join>, was indicted for that she, together with 
               <persName id="t17290827-32-person157">
                  Esther 
                  Morgan 
               <interp inst="t17290827-32-person157" type="surname" value="Morgan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17290827-32-person157" type="given" value="Esther"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17290827-32-person157" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
