            , not taken, did <rs id="t17290827-32-off146" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17290827-32-off146" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17290827-32-off146" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously steal a Gold Watch, Chain, and Seals, value 24 l. a Gold Snuff-Box, value 18 l. a Diamond Ear-ring, one Velvet Gown and Petticoat, and other Suits of silk Cloaths, and divers other wearing Apparel, Silk and Linen, as Head-Dress, Ruffles, Laces, &amp;c. to the Sum of 80 l. and 40 Guineas, the Goods of Martha Thorold, in the Dwelling-House of the said 
                     
                        <persName id="t17290827-32-victim159" type="victimName">
                           Martha 
                           Thorold 
                        <interp inst="t17290827-32-victim159" type="surname" value="Thorold"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17290827-32-victim159" type="given" value="Martha"></interp>
